Articles.Content:
2 hours ago, Checker_guy said:

I have been getting NRE every time I try to put parts in inventory (not NRE spam), just one at a time. Happening since the update.  

Could you please try removing all other mods but KIS&KAS? This is definitely a mods conflict issue but I cannot fix it until we figure out the conflicting mod.

UPD. Also, please look into KSP.log file for this error. There should be a stack trace which will tell us the source.

Edited May 26, 2016 by IgorZ

4 hours ago, IgorZ said:

Could you please try removing all other mods but KIS&KAS? This is definitely a mods conflict issue but I cannot fix it until we figure out the conflicting mod.

UPD. Also, please look into KSP.log file for this error. There should be a stack trace which will tell us the source.

After some trial and error, it seems to be Deadly Reentry preventing me from adding parts to the inventory. I am not quite sure why, but I have 56 other mods, and that seems to be the only thing conflicting with KIS. 

Log here:
